Package edu.sru.thangiah.datastructures.generic

Class AbstractTreeGeneric<T>

java.lang.Object
edu.sru.thangiah.datastructures.generic.AbstractTreeGeneric<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
BaseOpsGeneric<T>, TreeOpsGeneric<T>
Direct Known Subclasses:
AvlTreeGeneric, RedBlackTreeGeneric
public abstract class AbstractTreeGeneric<T> extends Object implements TreeOpsGeneric<T>

Title: AbstractTree

Description:

Abstract template for any general tree structure. TreeOpsInt, TreeTraversalOps and TreeSearchOps are inherited to layout the framework for the abstract class. This class can be inherited to allow for easy and standardized implementation of a tree
Version:
1.0
Author:
Sam R. Thangiah
